          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Permanent Department of Veterans Affairs Choice Card Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Veterans Access, Choice, and Accountability Act of 2014 to make the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) Choice Program permanent. (The program allows the furnishing of hospital care and medical services to eligible veterans through agreements with non-VA entities.)</p> <p>Eligibility requirements under the program are revised.</p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2016-02-18T20:17:23Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
